title: Episode 290: Eat & Block (Feat. Coi Leray)
itunes:title: Episode 290: Eat & Block (Feat. Coi Leray)
description:
Hip Hop artist, Coi Leray is here this week to promote her smash hit “No More Parties,” as well as her upcoming project. Coi discusses her issues with her father, Benzino, and the struggles of having to navigate the industry while being his daughter. On a lighter note, Coi gets candid about her past relationships with both men and women, she explains how she and Gunna got freaky in the car for the “Slide” music video, and much more. Coi even gets really vulnerable with the ladies, seeking advice for relationships moving forward. Enjoy!
